summary: AN ORDINANCE relating to the Yesler-Atlantic Neighborhood Improvement Project (No. Wash. R-5); authorizing acquisition of property in Blocks 22 and 23 of H. L. Yesler's 1st Addition to the City of Seattle, Blocks 6, 19 and 22 of Hill Tract Addition to the City of Seattle, and Blocks 3 and 5 of Jackson Street Addition to the City of Seattle.
